title: Jaguars Options at #1, Highest ceilings, Lack of QB buzz, and Which team will surprise everyone?
itunes:title: Jaguars Options at #1, Highest ceilings, Lack of QB buzz, and Which team will surprise everyone?
description:
The Good Morning Football Podcast begins with everyone still wondering who will be the top pick in the NFL Draft.  Hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Fmr NFL QB Matt Cassel discuss the Jaguars options and which player will have the highest ceiling.  The lack of buzz around QB's has surprised Peter and it could be the talk of Thursday night.  The table discusses which team will have them on their edge of their seats before making a pick and which team could flip the entire table on every team's plan with a surprise move.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
